name: AUDIO_MIXING_ERROR_TYPE
description:
Errors that might occur when playing a music
        file.

parameters.AUDIO_MIXING_ERROR_CAN_NOT_OPEN: The SDK cannot open the music file.

parameters.AUDIO_MIXING_ERROR_TOO_FREQUENT_CALL: The SDK opens the music file too frequently.

parameters.AUDIO_MIXING_ERROR_INTERRUPTED_EOF: The playback of the music file is interrupted.
